The new face of business advancement depends on Product Management, Data Science , and Blockchain Technology. Let’s first of all start with Product Management.
Product Management helps companies to produce the right products for consumers. With product Management, companies is able to strategize what kind of products to produce whether it’s a PAIN-KILLER or VITAMIN products.

     Secondly, Data Science also helps companies or businesses to plan, capture and analyze in other to make data-driven decisions to produce customer preference products. 

    Lastly, Blockchain Technology. After producing the right product for consumers with the help of data, the company would then leverage Blockchain Technology to build trust between the producer, distributor, and the final consumer. Blockchain helps companies to monitor how products and transactions moves between the life cycle of production. 
